  "prompt": "How do I change One Plus 3 ringtone?",
  "response": "To change the ringtone on a OnePlus 3, follow these steps:\n\n1. Open the \"Settings\" app on your phone\n\n2. Tap on \"Sound & notification\"\n\n3. Select \"Phone ringtone\"\n\n4. Choose from the default ringtones or tap \"Add\" to select a custom ringtone from your device storage\n\nAlternative method:\n1. Open the \"Music\" or \"File Manager\" app\n2. Find the audio file you want to use as a ringtone\n3. Long-press the file\n4. Select \"Set as ringtone\"\n\nFor contact-specific ringtones:\n1. Open \"Contacts\"\n2. Select a specific contact\n3. Tap the edit/pencil icon\n4. Choose \"Ringtone\" and select your preferred sound\n\nNote: Ensure the audio file is in a compatible format like MP3, and it's not too large in file size.",
